Package concurrentcube

Class CubeSide

  • java.lang.Object
    • concurrentcube.CubeSide
  • public class CubeSide
extends Object
    Class representing the side of a Cube. It consists of size * size fields of type Colour, and contains references to its neighbouring sides.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field Description
      private Colour[][] colours
      The fields of the side.
      private CubeSide[] neighbours
      References to the neighbouring sides in clockwise order.
      private CubeSide opposite
      The cube side opposite to this one.
      private int[] relativeRotations
      The rotations of the beginning positions of the neighbouring sides, relative to the rotation in which their uppermost rows runs along the border between it and this side.
      private int rotation
      Describes the number of times the side was rotated clockwise, relative to its beginning position, modulo 4.
      private int size
      The size of the cube.

                                          int layer,
                                          int index)

        Parameters:
